## Final Stack Summary
Layer	Framework
API	FastAPI
Agent orchestration	LangGraph
LLM	OpenAI API
Incident source	ServiceNow REST
Documentation	Confluence API
Task queue	Cloud Tasks / Celery
Database	PostgreSQL
Observability	OpenTelemetry
Metrics	Prometheus
Dashboard	Grafana
Logging	structlog
Container	Docker
Deployment	Cloud Run

## LLM Framework

Vertex AI / Gemini:
For:
summarization
RCA narrative
action item drafting
ambiguity classification

Not for:
MTTR
timeline ordering
CI validation

## Phase 2:
incident similarity detection
outage pattern discovery
auto remediation suggestions
reliability trend analysis

